title: Gjakova City Stadium
text: The City Stadium (, ) is a <a href="multi-use%20stadium">multi-use stadium</a> in <a href="Gjakova">Gjakova</a>, in western <a href="Kosovo">Kosovo</a>. It is used mostly for <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> matches and is the home ground of <a href="KF%20V%C3%ABllaznimi">KF Vëllaznimi</a> of the <a href="Kosovar%20Superliga">Kosovar Superliga</a>. The stadium has a capacity of 6,000 people.
